## 实验原理

### 空间多边形文件存储格式

可见后面附上的源文件示例。

#### obj 格式

每行一个字符 c 和三个数字 x、y、z 至文件末。当 c 为`v`时代表顶点，后面三个实数为顶点三维坐标；当 c 为`f`时代表平面，后面三个整数为顶点的索引。**索引下标从 1 开始**。

#### ply 格式

存在一个文件头，里面可以读出顶点数和平面数等信息；后续若干行分别按照文件头里的信息存放顶点坐标和平面索引。**索引下标从 0 开始**。

#### off 格式

类似于 ply 格式。**索引下标从 0 开始**。

#include <fstream>
#include <string>
#include <vector>
#include <GL/glut.h>
using namespace std;
typedef GLfloat lf;
struct Polyhedron
{
	struct Coord3
	{
		lf X, Y, Z;
	};
	struct Face
	{
		int v[3];
	};
	vector<Coord3> v;
	vector<Face> faces;
};
Polyhedron normal(Polyhedron m)
{
	lf ma = m.v[0].X, mi = ma;
	for (int i = 0; i < m.v.size(); ++i)
	{
		if (ma < m.v[i].X)
			ma = m.v[i].X;
		if (ma < m.v[i].Y)
			ma = m.v[i].Y;
		if (ma < m.v[i].Z)
			ma = m.v[i].Z;
		if (mi > m.v[i].X)
			mi = m.v[i].X;
		if (mi > m.v[i].Y)
			mi = m.v[i].Y;
		if (mi > m.v[i].Z)
			mi = m.v[i].Z;
	}
	for (int i = 0; i < m.v.size(); ++i)
	{
		m.v[i].X = (m.v[i].X - mi) / (ma - mi);
		m.v[i].Y = (m.v[i].Y - mi) / (ma - mi);
		m.v[i].Z = (m.v[i].Z - mi) / (ma - mi);
	}
	return m;
}
Polyhedron readOBJ(string s)
{
	Polyhedron mesh;
	for (fstream fin(s); fin >> s;)
	{
		if (s == "v")
		{
			Polyhedron::Coord3 vertex;
			fin >> vertex.X >> vertex.Y >> vertex.Z;
			mesh.v.push_back(vertex);
		}
		else if (s == "f")
		{
			Polyhedron::Face face;
			fin >> face.v[0] >> face.v[1] >> face.v[2];
			--face.v[0], --face.v[1], --face.v[2]; //OBJ下标从1开始的，这里做转换
			mesh.faces.push_back(face);
		}
	}
	return mesh;
}
Polyhedron readPLY(string s)
{
	Polyhedron mesh;
	ifstream fin(s);
	int vertex_num = 0, face_num = 0, num;
	while (fin >> s && s != "end_header")
		if (s == "element")
		{
			fin >> s >> num;
			if (s == "vertex")
				vertex_num = num;
			else if (s == "face")
				face_num = num;
		}
	for (int i = 0; i < vertex_num; ++i)
	{
		Polyhedron::Coord3 vertex;
		fin >> vertex.X >> vertex.Y >> vertex.Z;
		mesh.v.push_back(vertex);
	}
	for (int i = 0, num; i < face_num; ++i)
	{
		Polyhedron::Face face;
		fin >> num >> face.v[0] >> face.v[1] >> face.v[2];
		mesh.faces.push_back(face);
	}
	return mesh;
}
Polyhedron readOFF(string s)
{
	Polyhedron mesh;
	ifstream fin(s);
	int vertex_num, face_num, num;
	fin >> s >> vertex_num >> face_num >> num;
	for (int i = 0; i < vertex_num; ++i)
	{
		Polyhedron::Coord3 vertex;
		fin >> vertex.X >> vertex.Y >> vertex.Z;
		mesh.v.push_back(vertex);
	}
	for (int i = 0; i < face_num; ++i)
	{
		Polyhedron::Face face;
		fin >> num >> face.v[0] >> face.v[1] >> face.v[2];
		mesh.faces.push_back(face);
	}
	return mesh;
}

lf spin = 0, curX = 0, curY = -0.5, curZ = -2;
int typeNum = 0, modelNum = 0;
void display()
{
	glClear(GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT | GL_DEPTH_BUFFER_BIT);
	glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW);
	glLoadIdentity();
	glTranslatef(curX, curY, curZ);
	glRotatef(spin, 0, 1, 0);
	for (int i = 0; i < model.faces.size(); ++i)
	{
		Polyhedron::Coord3
			p0 = model.v[model.faces[i].v[0]],
			p1 = model.v[model.faces[i].v[1]],
			p2 = model.v[model.faces[i].v[2]];
		if (typeNum != 1)
		{
			glBegin(GL_LINES);
			glColor3f(1, 1, 1);
			glVertex3f(p0.X, p0.Y, p0.Z);
			glVertex3f(p1.X, p1.Y, p1.Z);
			glVertex3f(p0.X, p0.Y, p0.Z);
			glVertex3f(p2.X, p2.Y, p2.Z);
			glVertex3f(p1.X, p1.Y, p1.Z);
			glVertex3f(p2.X, p2.Y, p2.Z);
			glEnd();
		}
		if (typeNum != 2)
		{
			glBegin(GL_TRIANGLES);
			glColor3f(0, 1, 1);
			glVertex3f(p0.X, p0.Y, p0.Z);
			glColor3f(1, 0, 1);
			glVertex3f(p1.X, p1.Y, p1.Z);
			glColor3f(1, 1, 0);
			glVertex3f(p2.X, p2.Y, p2.Z);
			glEnd();
		}
	}

void keyboard(unsigned char key, int x, int y)
{
	if (key == 'w')
		curY += 0.1;
	else if (key == 'a')
		curX -= 0.1;
	else if (key == 's')
		curY -= 0.1;
	else if (key == 'd')
		curX += 0.1;
	else if (key == 'r')
		spin += 10;
	else if (key == 'e')
		typeNum = (typeNum + 1) % 3;
	else if (key == 'q')
	{
		modelNum = (modelNum + 1) % 3;
		if (modelNum == 0)
			model = normal(readOBJ("cow.obj"));
		else if (modelNum == 1)
			model = normal(readPLY("cactus.ply"));
		else
			model = normal(readOFF("Armadillo.off"));
	}
	else
		return;
	glutPostRedisplay();
}
void reshape(GLsizei w, GLsizei h)
{
	glViewport(0, 0, (GLsizei)w, (GLsizei)h);
	glMatrixMode(GL_PROJECTION);
	glLoadIdentity();
	gluPerspective(60, (GLfloat)w / (GLfloat)h, 1.0, 20);
	glMatrixMode(GL_MODELVIEW);
	glLoadIdentity();
	gluLookAt(1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 0);
}

{

	glutDisplayFunc(display);
	glutReshapeFunc(reshape);
	glutKeyboardFunc(keyboard);
	glutMainLoop();
}
